#id=1
#text=Being that we needed food in the house , I went through the cupboards and refrigerator to see what was there and made a list of what we needed .
#id=2
#text=We were almost out of food so it was a long list .
#id=3
#text=Then I drove to the grocery store .
#id=4
#text=First I went to the meat isle and picked out some juicy steaks and a chicken .
#id=5
#text=Then I went the the vegetable isle and picked out some fresh asparagus , broccoli , and salad fixings .
#id=6
#text=Next I went to the canned goods and picked out some cans to keep in the house .
#id=7
#text=I picked out some chili , soups and stews .
#id=8
#text=These are always good to have in the house for a quick meal .
#id=9
#text=Then I went to the dairy section and picked out some sour cream and milk .
#text=Then I pushed the cart to the payment isles and paid for the groceries .
